data.description: This charming 2-story home in West Point offers a comfortable and spacious living environment. With three bedrooms, it's perfect for those seeking extra space. The single bathroom is well-appointed and convenient. The home's design is both classic and inviting, with a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Located in the picturesque West Point area, close to shopping, Restaurants, Bear Mountain, and Palisades Parkway, it provides a peaceful and serene backdrop, making it an ideal place to call home. This home can also be a perfect investment property.
